All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
APIInterface
This interface represents all the API operations to be supported by the concrete implementation.
Constants
Class with all the constants that will be used across the different classes in this codebase and functions as a configuration file.
Controller
This interface represents all the operations to be supported by a controller implementation.
ControllerImpl
The controller implementation that receives all its inputs from an InputStream object and transmits all outputs to a PrintStream object.
CSVFile
This class represents files and its operations when it's data is comma-separated values(csv) format.
FileInterface
This interface represents all the I/O operations to be supported by a file database.
Main
This class serves as an entryway for the portfolio management program.
ModelImplementation
This class behaves as a gateway between model objects and operations and the controller and provides all model level functionalities to the controller interface from higher level.
ModelInterface
This interface represents all the Model operations to be supported by the concrete implementation and hides low level operations from whoever is trying to access information from file system or web api.
View
This interface represents all the operations to be supported by a view implementation.
ViewImpl
The controller implementation that receives all its inputs from an InputStream object and transmits all outputs to a PrintStream object.
WebAPI
This class represents web API and its operations when it's data is comma-separated values(csv) format.
